                 <strong>Police Verification Certificate (PVC):</strong><br><br>


                     <ul> 
                         <li>Residence proof</li>
<li>Photo ID proof</li>
<li>Document supporting need of PVC</li>
<li>Three passport size photographs</li>
<li>Copy of passport</li><br>
    <p>After applying the application is verified by local jurisdictional police station of the applicant. After getting clearance PVC is issued. To collect PVC applicant has to come in person to collect it along with original passport.</p>
